{"id": "art-315", "label": "Art. 315", "title": "Art. 315: Persoanele care nu pot fi ascultate ca martori", "slug": "art-315", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 315: Persoanele care nu pot fi ascultate ca martori </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Nu pot fi martori:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>1.rudele &#351;i afinii\npân&#259; la gradul al treilea inclusiv;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>2.so&#355;ul, fostul so&#355;,\nlogodnicul ori concubinul;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>3.cei afla&#355;i în\ndu&#351;m&#259;nie sau în leg&#259;turi de interese cu vreuna dintre\np&#259;r&#355;i;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_576748060\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1279\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_576748060\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>4.persoanele care beneficiaz&#259; de tutel&#259;\nspecial&#259;;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>5.cei condamna&#355;i pentru\nm&#259;rturie mincinoas&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)P&#259;r&#355;ile pot conveni,\nexpres sau tacit, s&#259; fie ascultate ca martori &#351;i persoanele\nprev&#259;zute la alin. (1) pct. 1-3.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1024823692\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1278\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1024823692\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Persoana care beneficiaz&#259; de consiliere\njudiciar&#259; poate fi ascultat&#259; ca martor, îns&#259; instan&#355;a va\n&#355;ine seama, la aprecierea depozi&#355;iei sale, de situa&#355;ia ei\nspecial&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}